Available Tools: list_processes | kill_process | get_process_info | top_processes
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "pid": "number", "name": "string", "signal": "string" }
Response Schema: { "processes": [{ "pid": "number", "name": "string", "cpu": "number", "mem": "number" }] }
---
Question: Show me the top 5 processes consuming the most CPU right now.
Call: { "func_call": "top_processes", "pid": null, "name": null, "signal": null }
Response: { "processes": [{ "pid": 1420, "name": "chrome", "cpu": 45.2, "mem": 12.4 }, { "pid": 890, "name": "firefox", "cpu": 32.1, "mem": 18.7 }, { "pid": 2301, "name": "node", "cpu": 28.5, "mem": 9.2 }, { "pid": 1105, "name": "python3", "cpu": 15.3, "mem": 6.8 }, { "pid": 304, "name": "docker", "cpu": 12.9, "mem": 14.1 }] }

